{"tid":1010798,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【等睇老貓gif】掟炮仗落坑渠點燃沼氣　貪玩女童遭炸斷手指","createTime":"2019-02-06T09:05:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-06T09:12:27.000Z","uid":54337,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"90fb76c8556fb7fc32af138909ebfd70a4dbb564","tid":1010798,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T09:05:59.000Z","msg":"掟炮仗落坑渠點燃沼氣　貪玩女童遭炸斷手指<br />\n<br />\n新年燒煙花、玩炮仗固然開心，但其危險性往往被人忽略。寧夏吳忠2名女童，周一（4日）下午就因為亂玩炮仗而發生意外受傷，其中1人更被炸斷手指。<br />\n<br />\n當日下午4時許，2名女童在街邊嬉戲時，疑因為一時貪玩，將點着的炮仗掟入坑渠，結果引起爆炸。網傳影片顯示，其中1名女童的右手拇指被炸至血肉模糊，一度暈倒在家人的懷中，而另1女童亦受傷躺在地上，據稱她們均無生命危險。"},{"pid":"2c8564ff5770c0fa85f204c45d83f9449afd219b","tid":1010798,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T09:06:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190206/mobile/bkn-20190206164935311-0206_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20190206%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190206164935311-0206_00952_001.html&d=fwxP8pl6u%2F9ArYBpkrNVTMQ0GhOv7yEvjYTsEPvBCF8%3D&h=f1764d49\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190206/mobile/bkn-20190206164935311-0206_00952_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"e1a6e274420ac86c037b27b8c11f2ea10808a115","tid":1010798,"uid":54337,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T09:09:27.000Z","msg":"小支支父母：牠只是個孩子呀"},{"pid":"f0fd2e0efffdacbe728cc18395b552d4112ce27a","tid":1010798,"uid":52459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T09:12:27.000Z","msg":"爆炸好麻煩，爆炸好麻煩，滿地炸彈"}]}